{"tid":1359371,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［學術］有冇邏輯入門書推薦？","createTime":"2019-07-24T06:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T12:38:15.000Z","uid":45926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cb941e8c9b4fd569a2b8900b48560de86fe3a1c7","tid":1359371,"uid":45926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:27:25.000Z","msg":"近排睇緊堆政哲書(The Prince)<br />\n想學下批判性思維<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c69dd9ea375bd1839179c165a1e462ca4a7d9e","tid":1359371,"uid":91771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:30:32.000Z","msg":"Introduction to logic<br />\nCopi &amp; Cohen<br />\n<br />\nCU philosophy year 1 邏輯學概論用書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Introduction-Logic-Irving-M-Copi/dp/1292024828\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FIntroduction-Logic-Irving-M-Copi%2Fdp%2F1292024828&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTe5mjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=73c11785\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Introduction-Logic-Irving-M-Copi/dp/1292024828</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/91zb4xFxwfL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F91zb4xFxwfL.jpg&h=2e8f05b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc451f6d89ba820f9261ec0add0d9f5241f95f0b","tid":1359371,"uid":126973,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:47:15.000Z","msg":"而家今時今日  學習點接收資訊<br />\n好過跟住d 死板嘅批判性思考嘅書<br />\n<br />\n點學習接收資訊 係要養成一個小心謹慎去檢視d講法，消息有冇好嘅根據<br />\n例如： <br />\n1) 講 &quot;fact-checked&quot; 唔代表有乜野 check 咗，<br />\n包括個 d 乜乜 tg 群組消息，<br />\n乜野錄音/對話 又話收到風云云。<br />\n細心考量任何資訊，說法有何證據，證據是否充分。<br />\n2) 唔好對接收嘅資訊作出反射性判斷，多加反覆細心思考。<br />\n3) 小心驗證自己本來已經相信嘅野：<br />\n有可能係一種 confirmation bias，<br />\n純屬自己一廂情願，然後選擇性收集，回憶解讀資訊。"},{"pid":"cda45f07e2eaccfd2da94c55ff8cc4ac76837e3f","tid":1359371,"uid