:"2019-07-24T12:48:46.000Z","msg":"我係中學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會唔會因為閲歷不足而睇唔明更深入嘅著作？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:11:37.000Z","msg":"冇架 由淺入深 上面介紹嘅書同文算比較入門<br />\n就算讀好多年都有好多野睇唔明 <br />\n慢慢求進步就可以"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:13:57.000Z","msg":"thx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打"},{"pid":"924bd0e8cdce82e34f6af00cc6bf880013f9e2e6","tid":1359371,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:34:03.000Z","msg":"兒子生性病母陪咁安慰"},{"pid":"f70b1c455a2e5bad91d16b3db486fa9392a2e8bc","tid":1359371,"uid":173852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:34:35.000Z","msg":"上面講得好，依度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係實際應用上<br />\n其實大部分好既議論文邏輯都唔複雜，好少用到太高級既推理技巧<br />\n用一般既細讀技巧，將背景、定義、論點、證據(證)搵哂出黎，睇佢有無跳步，或者點樣一步步論證個觀點，咁已經好夠<br />\n<br />\n任何議論文，無論你支持唔支持佢既立場，都要認真細讀分析<br />\n有D文觀點好，但論證一塌糊塗<br />\n有D文論證好，但原來定義上做左手腳，背景文代歪曲事實(大陸既文成日都係咁)<br />\n未必真係邏輯完全正確先叫好文章(否則數學論文就係最好既文章)，好多邏輯唔好既文章讀完都好有得著，但對一個好讀者而言，吃透每一篇文章既邏輯脈胳係必要的<br />\n(題外外話，其實古文都係要咁讀，乜章法、血脈、文氣，本身就係同文章既邏輯有關)<br />\n<br />\n對住細讀技巧既進一步討論，有本《如何閱讀一本書》，值得推介<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.books.com.tw/products/0010226097https://www.books.com.tw/products/0010226097\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.books.com.tw%2Fproducts%2F0010226097https%3A%2F%2Fwww.books.com.tw%2Fproducts%2F0010226097&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTe5mjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=77251ddf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.books.com.tw/products/0010226097https://www.books.com.tw/products/0010226097</a>"},{"pid":"acb9cc552b2a0d09d1de97615c7a633bf04d0168","tid":1359371,"uid":45926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f70b1c455a2e5bad91d16b3db486fa9392a2e8bc","tid":1359371,"uid":173852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:34:35.000Z","msg":"上面講得好，依度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係實際應用上<br />\n其實大部分好既議論文邏輯都唔複雜，好少用到太高級既推理技巧<br />\n用一般既細讀技巧，將背景、定義、論點、證據(證)搵哂出黎，睇佢有無跳步，或者點樣一步步論證個觀點，咁已經好夠<br />\n<br />\n任何議論文，無論你支持唔支持佢既立場，都要認真細讀分析<br />\n有D文觀點好，但論證一塌糊塗<br />\n有D文論證好，但原來定義上做左手腳，背景文代歪曲事實(大陸既文成日都係咁)<br />\n未必真係邏輯完全正確先叫好文章(否則數學論文就係最好既文章)，好多邏輯唔好既文章讀完都好有得著，但對一個好讀者而言，吃透每一篇文章既邏輯脈胳係必要的<br />\n(題外外話，其實古文都係要咁讀，乜章法、血脈、文氣，本身就係同文章既邏輯有關)<br />\n<br />\n對住細讀技巧既進一步討論，有本《如何閱讀一本書》，值得推介<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.books.com.tw/products/0010226097https://www.books.com.tw/products/0010226097\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.books.com.tw%2Fproducts%2F0010226097https%3A%2F%2Fwww.books.com.tw%2Fproducts%2F0010226097&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTe5mjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=77251ddf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.books.com.tw/products/0010226097https://www.books.com.tw/products/0010226097</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:54:39.000Z","msg":"我本身都有睇過how to read a book<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我睇到三分一見本書太囉嗦就用佢頭幾章教嗰個略讀技巧大致上睇一次成本書就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇做分析閲讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"993e07f448da24a9fdf1a02d14376c868d20af5b","tid":1359371,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acb9cc552b2a0d09d1de97615c7a633bf04d0168","tid":1359371,"uid":45926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f70b1c455a2e5bad91d16b3db486fa9392a2e8bc","tid":1359371,"uid":173852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:34:35.000Z","msg":"上面講得好，依度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係實際應用上<br />\n其實大部分好既議論文邏輯都唔複雜，好少用到太高級既推理技巧<br />\n用一般既細讀技巧，將背景、定義、論點、證據(證)搵哂出黎，睇佢有無跳步，或者點樣一步步論證個觀點，咁已經好夠<br />\n<br />\n任何議論文，無論你支持唔支持佢既立場，都要認真細讀分析<br />\n有D文觀點好，但論證一塌糊塗<br />\n有D文論證好，但原來定義上做左手腳，背景文代歪曲事實(大陸既文成日都係咁)<br />\n未必真係邏輯完全正確先叫好文章(否則數學論文就係最好既文章)，好多邏輯唔好既文章讀完都好有得著，但對一個好讀者而言，吃透每一篇文章既邏輯脈胳係必要的<br />\n(題外外話，其實古文都係要咁讀，乜章法、血脈、文氣，本身就係同文章既邏輯有關)<br />\n<br />\n對住細讀技巧既進一步討論，有本《如何閱讀一本書》，值得推介<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.books.com.tw/products/0010226097https://www.books.com.tw/products/0010226097\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.books.com.tw%2Fproducts%2F0010226097https%3A%2F%2Fwww.books.com.tw%2Fproducts%2F0010226097&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTe5mjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=77251ddf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.books.com.tw/products/0010226097https://www.books.com.tw/products/0010226097</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:54:39.000Z","msg":"我本身都有睇過how to read a book<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我睇到三分一見本書太囉嗦就用佢頭幾章教嗰個略讀技巧大致上睇一次成本書就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇做分析閲讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:22:18.000Z","msg":"依度估一下 巴打本身睇書係唔會筆過（做note)既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf8c4e99eef1dcc38293ce73110360d0b6cad890","tid":1359371,"uid":45926,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"993e07f448da24a9fdf1a02d14376c868d20af5b","tid":1359371,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acb9cc552b2a0d09d1de97615c7a633bf04d0168","tid":1359371,"uid":45926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f70b1c455a2e5bad91d16b3db486fa9392a2e8bc","tid":1359371,"uid":173852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:34:35.00